      <title>CenterPoint 因飓风 Beryl 导致休斯顿停电而被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/centerpoint-sued-over-hurricane-beryl-power-outages-in-houston</link>
      <description><![CDATA[休斯顿的一些餐馆在飓风贝丽尔 (Hurricane Beryl) 过后停电数天，他们起诉了该市的主要公用事业公司，指控 CenterPoint Energy Inc. 未能对基础设施进行充分投资，也没有对大面积停电做出反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-16/centerpoint-sued-over-hurricane-beryl-power-outages-in-houston</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jul 2024 13:46:03 GMT</pubDate>
